==Translingual==

===Etymology===
From the Greek [[ἄρθρον]] (''arthron'', meaning ''joint'') and [[πούς]]/[[ποδός]] (''pous/podos'' meaning ''foot'').

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Arthropoda'''
#a [[taxonomic]] [[phylum]], within [[superphylum]] [[Protostomia]] &mdash; the [[arthropod]]s

